{
  "stem": "25809.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the first reaction-- I hadn't seen anything like that since, since the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when I saw this, it totally, it completely threw me, threw me back physically almost a couple of steps.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I did a couple of steps backwards to, to absorb this, this impact of this Jewish star that I had worn.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And maybe later on, I can explain to you why it meant so much to me, because I was wearing it for many-- for, for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anyhow, we'll come to that later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not particularly, except that my mother did a good job in sewing stars on different outer garments that I would be wearing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In general, there was no reactions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There, there was no reactions in general.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody ever said anything to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- my, my character is very accepting and phlegmatic to a certain degree.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I felt, OK, if that's what I have to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a little kid, what are you going to say?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, well we have to wear this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, all right, now, I just accepted it without any, any argument.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I knew that I could not argue about the matter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I had non-Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, at that age, I never looked at friends whether they were Jewish or non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was totally unimportant for me at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, there were situations where I was being-- I remember there was one situation where some kids were kind of, yeah, yeah, yeah, you're a Jew, you're a Jew, you're-- and things like that, were hollering at me.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then one day-- and I told my father about that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father said, well, he said, I want to know more about that.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
